<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="603" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="6.[1358,2566,1474,2139]" pageId="6" pageNumber="603">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1360,1720,1986,2020]" pageId="6" pageNumber="603">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Not yet assessed on The IUCN Red List. The Muze Spiny Mouse seems to have a relatively large distribution and can be found in numerous protected areas.
</paragraph>
